# macOS system files

.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.fseventsd
.VolumeIcon.icns
.com.apple.timemachine.donotpresent
.com.apple.metadata:*

## Temporary/backup files (general)

*~
*.bak
*.tmp
*.old
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
*.asd
*.orig

## Word/Excel temp files

~$*
*.wbk         # Word backup
*.xlk         # Excel backup
*.tmp         # Office temp
*.lock        # File lock indicators

## Affinity autosave/backup (safe to ignore)

*.autosave
*.afdesign-preview
*.afphoto-preview
*.afpub-preview

## Template files
# These lines are commented out by default, meaning the template files
# (.tex, .lua, .yaml, .sh) ARE tracked by Git.
